                                    <p>The tablet is nscribed on <rs type="sides" key="opisthographic">both sides</rs>. It preserves another inscription on the same side (<ref target="i-dodone-online-7b">7B</ref>), with respect to which the present text is inscribed upside down. The present text overlaps the last line of <ref target="i-dodone-online-7b">7B</ref>, rendering its final letters illegible. On the opposite side, two inscriptions (<ref target="i-dodone-online-5a">5A</ref> and <ref target="i-dodone-online-6a">6A</ref>), together with traces of earlier texts, are preserved.</p>
